description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Anurak purrs with a rating of 42, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 210, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 2 for East, Leverage for South, and Nine Lives for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20425-82693-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [210 Votes, Top 5% Score]
